{"tid":2361353,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗天水圍村屋上車盤討論","createTime":"2021-01-10T14:34:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-17T11:58:27.000Z","uid":385855,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c0315564ff2db956e7866503a65e990768eb34ab","tid":2361353,"uid":385855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T14:34:19.000Z","msg":"最近睇緊元朗天水圍嘅村屋，睇中咗厦村嗰邊嗰幾個地點：厦村錫降圍、富怡花園同埋沙洲里村<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n貪佢地唔太入 同埋仲行到去天水圍市。有冇巴絲知道呢三個地方有冇啲咩古怪嘢？因為上網睇啲兇宅查詢都係得啲好大路嘅新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋仲有冇啲咩地方好似果幾個地方咁嘅地段同價錢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：有養狗狗 筆直唔多 想搵下啲三球到三球半左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbab77b0ef999957972531744218cffdf31742a9","tid":2361353,"uid":376326,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T14:34:56.000Z","msg":"721夠唔夠古怪？"},{"pid":"1c82c0ad4ec4429c62eb5935bee127598b6c067f","tid":2361353,"uid":58880,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T14:44:00.000Z","msg":"元朗都睇？想比人斬定扑爆架車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5135c363cf1b91eb2275ae2ba334665b323b55d","tid":2361353,"uid":385855,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"1c82c0ad4ec4429c62eb5935bee127598b6c067f","tid":2361353,"uid":58880,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T14:44:00.000Z","msg":"元朗都睇？想比人斬定扑爆架車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T15:22:40.000Z","msg":"冇事嘅應該 都一直搵開屋苑形式嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又見到果頭好多後生住緊 反而擔心有冇咩兇宅而新聞又冇咩點提到"},{"pid":"cafd8b4a3a5cde69bea79ccf6ca7f62258bacc26","tid":2361353,"uid":277888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":